# Instacart Customer Behavior Analysis

## Project Overview
This project analyzes customer purchasing behavior using Instacart grocery order data.

## Objectives
• Understand purchasing patterns
• Identify popular products
• Analyze reorder behavior

## Tools
Python
Pandas
Matplotlib
Seaborn

## Dataset
Instacart Market Basket Analysis dataset.

## Key Insights
• Most orders happen during weekends
• Certain product categories have high reorder rates
